      "text": "Error Flows:\n  400 ALIAS_FEATURE_DISABLED — feature flag off\n  400 INVALID_ALIAS — bad format or reserved word\n  409 ALIAS_TAKEN — pre-check or UNIQUE constraint violation\n  429 RATE_LIMIT_EXCEEDED — >2 req/min custom alias",
